N.Y. Comp. Codes R. & Regs. Tit. 9 ยง 1811.1 - Notification

State Regulations

The municipal urban renewal agency, or municipality, within 30 days of approval by HUD of its certificate of completion and of gross
and net project cost, shall notify the commissioner in writing of such
approval. Notes
